{"data":[{"date":"09:17 15/08","title":"Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khen ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/15/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edd b\u00e1o th\u1ec3 thao ch\u00e2u \u00c1 theo d\u00f5i s\u00e1t sao c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam ASIAD 2018 v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\u0110o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng 3-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Pakistan \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n m\u00f4n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018. V\u1edbi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ec1u, \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, trang FOX Sports phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n ch\u00e2u \u00c1 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen t\u1eb7ng cho V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. Trong b\u00e0i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e2y b\u00fat Gabriel Tan cho r\u1eb1ng, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111ang d\u1ea7n thay \u0111\u1ed5i tri\u1ebft l\u00fd ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c, s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/vn-15342604637281618228882.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng, t\u1ea1o th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o so v\u1edbi Pakistan v\u00e0 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 3-0. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f4ng, nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 l\u01b0\u1eddng. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd g\u00e2y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 d\u1ec5 cho Nepal l\u1eabn Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Gabriel Tan, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 nh\u1ecf con Quang H\u1ea3i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn danh hi\u1ec7u C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u khi ch\u01a1i b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9, s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o d\u00f9 b\u1ecb k\u00e9o xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ea5p d\u01b0\u1edbi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edd Sohu c\u1ee7a Trung Qu\u1ed1c th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh, Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh huy ch\u01b0\u01a1ng ASIAD. \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m. M\u1ecdi con s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec1u cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd so v\u1edbi Pakistan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Quang H\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 Messi c\u1ee7a Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc, t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1eeb gi\u1ea3i ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 ASIAD. Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 cho c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSiamSport c\u0169ng so s\u00e1nh gi\u1eefa U23 Th\u00e1i Lan v\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Asiad: \"U23 Th\u00e1i Lan ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb Qatar.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n kh\u00e1c \u1edf \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 l\u00e0 U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 h\u01b0ng ph\u1ea5n sau th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. H\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c v\u00e0 nghi\u1ec1n n\u00e1t U23 Pakistan 3-0.\"<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng t\u1edd b\u00e1o nh\u01b0 Goal phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n Th\u00e1i Lan, STN Sports c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i ph\u00e2n t\u00edch, \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng, s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u00f9ng kh\u00e1t khao chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng s\u1ebd gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfn xa.<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c tin b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 d\u01b0 \u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-ke-hoach-tap-luyen-sau-tran-thang-pakistan-168-194505.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam thay \u0111\u1ed5i k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Pakistan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/cong-phuong-khong-con-co-hoi-da-11m-duoi-thoi-hlv-park-hang-seo-168-194504.html\">C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 11m d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Park Hang Seo?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-292-194503.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-khi-cong-phuong-hai-lan-da-hong-phat-den-168-194501.html\">C\u00e1c chuy\u00ean gia n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sergio-aguero-cung-tung-hai-lan-da-hong-11m-trong-mot-tran-dau-nhu-cong-phuong-168-194500.html\">Sergio Aguero c\u0169ng t\u1eebng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng 11m trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/van-quyet-noi-do-cho-cong-phuong-sau-man-da-tham-hoa-168-194499.html\">V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft n\u00f3i \u0111\u1ee1 cho C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5515","checkdouble":"194524"},{"date":"09:40 15/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 15/8: Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/diem-tin-sang-158-paul-scholes-nhan-xet-buon-ve-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU, Tottenham d\u1eddi ng\u00e0y m\u1edf c\u1eeda SV\u0110,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 15/8.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1eddi m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi sang Juventus c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n Cristiano Ronaldo, Marcelo kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \"gi\u1edd ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i l\u00fac n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y\" khi \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Real Madrid chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Atletico t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 158 Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 158 Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t bu\u1ed3n v\u1ec1 MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/scholes.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Paul Scholes \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u1ee7a Man Utd.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng Paul Scholes nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t r\u1eb1ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Man Utd v\u1eabn \"r\u1ea5t nh\u1ecf b\u00e9\", b\u1edfi ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh v\u1eabn k\u00e9m so v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 Liverpool.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 37 tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0ng Samuel Eto'o ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng. \"B\u00e1o \u0111en\" m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Qatar SC, m\u1ed9t CLB t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Qatar. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 CLB th\u1ee9 13 trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a Eto'o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1eb3ng ai \u1edf Liverpool ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Naby Keita trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi West Ham, b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Guinea t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t l\u00e2u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Premier League c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0a th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n ch\u1ed1t s\u1ed5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 m\u1ed1c 31/8, khi c\u00e1c CLB s\u1ebd b\u1ecf phi\u1ebfu trong cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp s\u1eafp t\u1edbi. \u1ede m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018, k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Premier League k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 9/8, tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Koke cho r\u1eb1ng ngay c\u1ea3 khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, Real Madrid v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nguy hi\u1ec3m n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Atletico ph\u1ea3i c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u1ea3nh gi\u00e1c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ghi b\u00e0n g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-0 c\u1ee7a Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc Huddersfield \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, N'Golo Kante kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 d\u01b0 v\u1ecb c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 \u1edf ph\u00eda sau \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"San moi cua Tottenham dang trong qua trinh hoan thien va du kien mo cua vao ngay 15/9.\" title=\"S\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn m\u1edf c\u1eeda v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/9.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Chuyen-nhuong-Tottenham-he-2018-Mua-khong-noi,-ban-chang-xong!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>S\u00e2n m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Tottenham \u0111ang trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n v\u00e0 s\u1ebd m\u1edf c\u1eeda mu\u1ed9n h\u01a1n so v\u1edbi d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ban \u0111\u1ea7u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTottenham d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ph\u1ea3i d\u1eddi th\u1eddi gian m\u1edf c\u1eeda s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng m\u1edbi do v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 an to\u00e0n, thay v\u00ec l\u1ecbch d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 15/9. Tottenham \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ed1n kho\u1ea3ng 800 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y SV\u0110 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ec7nh danh l\u00e0 \"hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League 2018-19, Luke Shaw g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u00fap Man Utd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Leicester v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 2-1. Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 b\u00ed quy\u1ebft ch\u01a1i hay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, Luke Shaw cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi\u00a0Jonny Marsh, chuy\u00ean gia dinh d\u01b0\u1ee1ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi De Bruyne, Kyle Walker v\u00e0 John Terry \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u00e2n n\u1eb7ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Gabi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \"c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn\" khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Thibaut Courtois kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Real Madrid.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn trong bu\u1ed5i s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 15/8:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truyen-thong-chau-a-khen-ngoi-chien-thang-cua-olympic-viet-nam-o-asiad-2018-168-194524.html\">Truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng ch\u00e2u \u00c1 khen ng\u1ee3i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u1edf ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-liverpool-khong-phai-so-mot-nhung-se-danh-bai-so-mot-172-194517.html\">Klopp: Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-atletico-madrid-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-gia-nhap-man-utd-172-194516.html\">Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu-184-194514.html\">Lionel Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jurgen-klopp-canh-bao-liverpool-172-194513.html\">Jurgen Klopp c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Liverpool:West Ham \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i M.U hay Man City</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5514","checkdouble":"194526"},{"date":"10:29 15/08","title":"Diego Simeone ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/diego-simeone-truoc-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mang t\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><h2>Quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng x\u00fac c\u1ea3m<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2 2018 gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Atletico Madri mang r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Julen Lopetegui, sau s\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a HLV Zinedine Zidane v\u00e0 si\u00eau sao Cristiano Ronaldo trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/diego-simeone-truoc-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 ch\u1ec9 ra y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ec3 Thibaut Courtois t\u00e1i ng\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico trong th\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u, n\u01a1i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u01b0 ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay. Th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Gabi c\u1ee7a Atletico th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Courtois tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 mang \u0111\u1ebfn \"n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone tr\u01b0\u1edbc Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t: \"\u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 c\u1ea3m x\u00fac v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac t\u1eeb ch\u00ednh nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 l\u1ea1c quan<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Atletico Madrid gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Antoine Griezmann, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi b\u1ed5 sung nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Gelson Martins, Thomas Lemar hay Santiago Arias. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Diego Simeone cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ee7 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"S\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o cho s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0ng ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t l\u00ean ngay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp\" - HLV Simeone \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1: \"R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u00e2n s\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ed1ng h\u1ecd\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng thua k\u00e9m ai h\u1ebft. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebfn th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn theo nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Diego Simeone s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y khi v\u1eabn v\u01b0\u1edbng \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft t\u1ea1i Europa League g\u1eb7p Arsenal. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Atletico s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Atletico Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-atletico-madrid-tiet-lo-ly-do-tu-choi-gia-nhap-man-utd-172-194516.html\">Sao Atletico Madrid ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia nh\u1eadp Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-valencia-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-atletico-madrid-180-194372.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Valencia chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Atletico Madrid</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-madrid-chinh-thuc-co-tien-dao-moi-180-194137.html\">Atletico Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-bat-ngo-chuyen-huong-sang-godin-172-194125.html\">MU t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Atletico</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/atletico-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-tien-dao-moi-180-193893.html\">Atletico \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5513","checkdouble":"194528"},{"date":"10:57 15/08","title":"Lopetegui: \"Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Real\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/lopetegui-zidane-da-la-qua-khu-voi-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Zidane \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 v\u1edbi Real Madrid v\u00e0 b\u00e0y t\u1ecf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m vi\u1ebft n\u00ean m\u1ed9t ch\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi huy ho\u00e0ng h\u01a1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Zidane \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau khi \u0111\u01b0a Real Madrid t\u1edbi 3 ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay sau \u0111\u00f3, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00ean l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Zidane. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, sau khi th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha sa th\u1ea3i ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 51 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean c\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ecb HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Real. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Tallinn v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/lopetegui-zidane-da-la-qua-khu-voi-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Lopetegui ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Zidane tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn, Lopetegui r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real \u1edf m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng t\u1ed1t sau khi Zidane ra \u0111i. Nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng c\u0169ng b\u00e0y t\u1ecf mong mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean sau tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cZizou \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u phi th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u cao qu\u00fd. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u, l\u00e0m n\u00ean l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch m\u1edbi v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i ph\u00eda sau. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfn l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nReal v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf sau khi b\u00e1n Ronaldo \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u0111\u00f3, Gareth Bale v\u00e0 Karim Benzema \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch m\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cBale l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf Real \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m v\u00e0 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 ngay t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c l\u1edbn v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9. T\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 mu\u1ed1n n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 l\u00fac n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y th\u00edch th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Bale. T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 l\u00e0 Benzema. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi ph\u01b0\u01a1ng di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u1ed1t ngay t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ea7u t\u00f4i m\u1edbi t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y lu\u00f4n t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Real:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo-180-194511.html\">Sergio Ramos: Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5512","checkdouble":"194529"},{"date":"10:48 15/08","title":"Ramos tr\u1ea5n an Courtois tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/ramos-tran-an-courtois-truoc-man-ra-mat-lan-lon-cam-xuc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Real Madrid r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00eam nay, \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico Madrid.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng cho Thibaut Courtois khi anh to\u1ea1i nguy\u1ec7n gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00eam nay v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Courtois s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid v\u00e0 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh trong khung g\u1ed7 ngay t\u1eeb ban \u0111\u1ea7u. Run r\u1ee7i thay, \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 Atletico Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/ramos-tran-an-courtois-truoc-man-ra-mat-lan-lon-cam-xuc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois tr\u1eadn Real Madrid vs Atletico Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea n\u0103m 2014, Courtois tr\u1ea3i qua ba m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc \u1edf Vicente Calderon, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u01b0 khi th\u00e2u t\u00f3m \u0111\u1ee7 c\u1ea3 La Liga, Copa del Rey, Europa League v\u00e0 Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e0nh ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i v\u1ec1 nh\u00ec ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Real Madrid \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2013-14.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i 180 \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ec9 sau 4 n\u0103m v\u00e0 gi\u1edd, Courtois s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 ng\u00e0y n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft l\u1eabn l\u1ed9n c\u1ea3m x\u00fac cho c\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea v\u00e0 th\u1ea5u hi\u1ec3u \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u1ea5n an tinh th\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 hay quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 c\u1ee7a ai \u0111\u00f3. Quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid v\u00e0 tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp, th\u00edch nghi v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 t\u00e2m l\u00fd nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng ai c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n g\u00ec m\u00e0 ph\u00e1n x\u00e9t vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Atletico h\u1ebft c\u1ea3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nhan-dinh-real-madrid-vs-atletico-2h00-ngay-158-diem-ket-cho-mot-the-he-180-194518.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid vs Atletico (2h00 ng\u00e0y 16/8): \u0110i\u1ec3m k\u1ebft cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7?</span><br>\r\nCu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi si\u00eau sao s\u1ed1...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5511","checkdouble":"194531"},{"date":"09:22 15/08","title":"Klopp: \"Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t, nh\u01b0ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/klopp-liverpool-khong-phai-so-mot-nhung-se-danh-bai-so-mot.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Manchester City m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 h\u1ea1 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau li\u00ean t\u1ee5c gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh, Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi c\u01a1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00ean ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 m\u00f2n m\u1ecfi \u0111\u1ee3i ch\u1edd. Th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i c\u00e0ng khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c Kopites v\u1eefng tin v\u00e0o vinh quang r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 n\u0103m nay.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool Man City m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool Man City m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/13/klopp-liverpool-khong-phai-so-mot-nhung-se-danh-bai-so-mot.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, Liverpool s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n h\u1ea1 b\u1ec7 nh\u00e0 t\u00e2n v\u01b0\u01a1ng Manchester City m\u00e0 theo th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh HLV Jurgen Klopp, \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecd. Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u:<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd mu\u1ed1n nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. T\u00f4i quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u00e2ng cao ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u00ecnh d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u0169ng b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 Liverpool m\u1edbi c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i nh\u01b0ng t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, t\u00f4i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Man City v\u1eabn l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, Liverpool \u0111ang th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 l\u00e0 kh\u1eafc tinh c\u1ee7a Man City khi to\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League. L\u00fac n\u00e0y sau v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19, The Kop c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u BXH sau m\u00e0n h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t West Ham \u0111\u1ebfn 4-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien-172-194354.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien-172-194354.html\">Liverpool h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t West Ham: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n?</span><br>\r\nLiverpool ch\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ed1n sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham, b\u1eafn ph\u00e1t ph\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u cho c\u1ea3 Premier League r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ngai...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5510","checkdouble":"194517"},{"date":"09:54 15/08","title":"Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Mbappe th\u1ee9 hai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/2/than-dong-chelsea-co-the-tro-thanh-mbappe-thu-hai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Jonathan Pazon d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi c\u00f3 c\u00e1nh g\u1eedi t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Callum Hudson-Odoi ng\u00f4i sao 17 tu\u1ed5i m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i \u1edf s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 Eden Hazard, Olivier Giroud hay Willian \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 mu\u1ed9n sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb v\u00f4 danh Callum Hudson-Odoi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2n HLV Maurizio Sarri trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i v\u00e0 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c C\u0110V Chelsea.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Hudson-Odoi c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Hudson-Odoi c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/than-dong-chelsea-co-the-tro-thanh-mbappe-thu-hai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb Hudson-Odoi c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Mbappe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi 17 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y c\u0169ng khi\u1ebfn ngay c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e0n anh Alvaro Morata ph\u1ea3i h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c kinh ng\u1ea1c. C\u1ef1u ng\u00f4i sao Real Madrid t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i t\u00e1c m\u0103ng non c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng The Blues: \u201cTh\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o nh\u01b0 Callum, c\u1ee9 nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 25-26 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1edbi 17 v\u1eady!\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">G\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t, Hudson-Odoi th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00e2ng b\u1ed1c cao h\u01a1n l\u00ean m\u00e2y xanh khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Kylian Mbappe, ng\u00f4i sao tu\u1ed5i teen c\u1ee7a Paris Saint-Germain xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 m\u1edbi g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 Jonathan Panzo, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi r\u1eddi Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Monaco h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc: \u201cCallum l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi hay nh\u1ea5t ng\u00e0y t\u00f4i m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y. Khi l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ch\u00fat, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i h\u01a1n, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 ch\u1eefng ch\u1ea1c v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin kh\u00e1c th\u01b0\u1eddng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cNh\u1eefng g\u00ec Callum \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, \u0111\u01a1n c\u1eed nh\u01b0 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t, ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. T\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn r\u1ed3i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u00ea d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Callum g\u1ee3i nh\u1edb t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn Mbappe.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5509","checkdouble":"194521"},{"date":"09:43 15/08","title":"Bakayoko tri \u00e2n Chelsea sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/bakayoko-tri-an-chelsea-sau-khi-gia-nhap-ac-milan.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bakayoko \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi tri \u00e2n cho Chelsea sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan thi \u0111\u1ea5u theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bakayoko gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i theo m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 5 n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Conte v\u00e0o giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a HLV Maurizio Sarri gi\u00fap Bakayoko c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i kh\u00f4i ph\u1ee5c s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p \u1edf Chelsea. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn AC Milan theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Bakayoko tri \u00e2n Chelsea sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Bakayoko tri \u00e2n Chelsea sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/bakayoko-tri-an-chelsea-sau-khi-gia-nhap-ac-milan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Bakayoko tri \u00e2n Chelsea sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AC\u00a0Milan</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMilan c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Bakayoko v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y mong mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Chelsea t\u1ea1i Premier League h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fac gia \u0111\u00ecnh Chelsea c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. H\u1eb9n g\u1eb7p l\u1ea1i\u201d, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Monaco chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean trang Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAC Milan, c\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 t\u00f4i v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y\u201d, Bakayoko chia s\u1ebb trong m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i \u0111\u0103ng kh\u00e1c.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Sarri t\u1eebng \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Bakayoko l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1eddi Chelsea h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. V\u00e0 qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c Bakayoko c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u00dd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea b\u00e2y gi\u1edd qu\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4ng. V\u1eady n\u00ean t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft ai s\u1ebd ra \u0111i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1eeb 23-24 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f9ng 3 ho\u1eb7c 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Bakayoko ra \u0111i? C\u00f3 th\u1ec3. B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i h\u1ecfi ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/than-dong-chelsea-co-the-tro-thanh-mbappe-thu-hai-172-194521.html\">Th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Mbappe th\u1ee9 hai</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-ac-milan-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-chelsea-172-194493.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: AC Milan chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sao Chelsea</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5508","checkdouble":"194523"},{"date":"10:27 15/08","title":"Klopp c\u00f3 l\u1eddi nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/30/klopp-co-loi-nhan-gui-hang-tien-ve-chat-choi-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf Anfield.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 g\u00e2y n\u00e1o lo\u1ea1n th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Liverpool \u0111\u00f3n v\u1ec1 th\u00eam hai ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ea3 tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng l\u00e0 Naby Keita v\u00e0 Fabinho, n\u00e2ng s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 khu trung t\u00e2m l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 7, bao g\u1ed3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eefng Jordan Henderson, Georginio Wijnaldum, James Milner, Alex Oxlade-Chamberlain v\u00e0 Adam Lallana.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/klopp-co-loi-nhan-gui-hang-tien-ve-chat-choi-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Klopp nh\u1eafn g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadt ch\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111ang g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay Emre Can \u0111\u00e3 ra \u0111i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Juventus, cu\u1ed9c c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00e1c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u1edf Anfield v\u1eabn v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng g\u1eaft gao v\u00e0 kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 ai, HLV Jurgen Klopp qua \u0111\u00e2y mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean v\u00e0 th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u cho ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c: \u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i tinh th\u1ea7n t\u00edch c\u1ef1c, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i ai trong s\u1ed1 h\u1ecd c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t l\u00fac n\u00e0y. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ng\u1eebng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1eadp ra \u0111\u1ebfn ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, nh\u01b0 Naby r\u1ed3i Gini v\u00e0 Millie \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ebfn 13km trong tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng West Ham. \u0110\u00fang v\u1eady, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 4-0 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng nh\u01b0 anh ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201c\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u00f4i l\u00fac n\u00e0o c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u1edf c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u2013 s\u1ef1 ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9 v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec7t huy\u1ebft. C\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng Hendo hay Adam n\u1eefa, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm mu\u1ed9n m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho Liverpool, t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1i \u0111\u00f3.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n sau, Liverpool h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn London l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a Crystal Palace v\u1edbi m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng Premier League, trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien-172-194354.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/13/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-thang-west-ham-doi-bong-manh-nhat-da-lo-dien-172-194354.html\">Liverpool h\u1ee7y di\u1ec7t West Ham: \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ed9 di\u1ec7n?</span><br>\r\nLiverpool ch\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19 b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1ed1n sao tr\u01b0\u1edbc West Ham, b\u1eafn ph\u00e1t ph\u00e1o hi\u1ec7u cho c\u1ea3 Premier League r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ngai v\u00e0ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5507","checkdouble":"194530"},{"date":"11:14 15/08","title":"Barca l\u1ea1i khi\u1ebfn MU \u0111\u1ee9ng ng\u1ed3i kh\u00f4ng y\u00ean v\u1edbi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Pogba","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/11/barca-lai-khien-mu-dung-ngoi-khong-yen-voi-phat-bieu-ve-pogba.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu th\u00ec gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Ariedo Braida c\u0169ng \u00fap m\u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng cu\u1ed7m ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t Old Trafford v\u1ec1 Camp Nou trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca mua Pogba t\u1eeb MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Tranh th\u1ee7 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p gi\u1eefa Paul Pogba v\u00e0 Jose Mourinho c\u00f9ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh mu\u1ed1n chia tay Man Utd c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Barcelona l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 n\u00e0y. S\u1ef1 ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Andres Iniesta c\u00e0ng th\u00f4i th\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch thay th\u1ebf anh b\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 G\u0110TT c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Pogba t\u1eeb MU h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch v\u00e0 G\u0110TT c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Barca mua Pogba t\u1eeb MU h\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/11/Barca-len-tieng-vu-chi-130-trieu-bang-mua-Paul-Pogba-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca mua Pogba t\u1eeb MU trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi v\u1eady m\u00e0 g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Josep Maria Bartomeu \u00fap m\u1edf quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb b\u1ecf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 bom t\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ea5n n\u00e0y trong kho\u1ea3ng g\u1ea7n ba tu\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8 n\u0103m nay, kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t t\u00e2n binh n\u1eefa nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 danh t\u00ednh nh\u1eb1m t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u00e1c CLB kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Ariedo Braida c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng ti\u1ebfp l\u1eddi l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o tr\u00ean th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng Camp Nou khi tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1i t\u00ean Pogba, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u00f4ng n\u00f3i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 h\u1eb5ng c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i m\u01a1 h\u1ed3. B\u00e1o ch\u00ed d\u1eabn l\u1eddi ng\u1eafn g\u1ecdn: \u201cPogba l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi m\u00e0 m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y hay kh\u00f4ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 n\u0103m nay, Barca \u0111\u00e3 chi ra kho\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 140 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 4 t\u00e2n binh, bao g\u1ed3m Arthur Melo, Clement Lenglet, Malcom v\u00e0 Arturo Vidal. N\u1ebfu k\u00edch n\u1ed5 qu\u1ea3 si\u00eau bom t\u1ea5n Pogba, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn con s\u1ed1 chi ti\u00eau s\u1ebd c\u00e1n m\u1ed1c 300 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a g\u00e3 kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 x\u1ee9 Catalonia v\u01b0\u1ee3t m\u1eb7t Liverpool trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-doi-roi-man-utd-ai-la-ke-dung-sau-giat-day-172-194179.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/paul-pogba-doi-roi-man-utd-ai-la-ke-dung-sau-giat-day.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-doi-roi-man-utd-ai-la-ke-dung-sau-giat-day-172-194179.html\">Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Man Utd: Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ee9ng sau gi\u1eadt d\u00e2y?</span><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Man Utd d\u00f9 th\u1eadt hay gi\u1ea3 v\u1eabn t\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9ng ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c l\u00ean qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Li\u1ec7u Pogba c\u00f3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i? Ai l\u00e0 k\u1ebb \u0111\u1ee9ng sau m\u00e0n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5506","checkdouble":"194533"},{"date":"07:23 15/08","title":"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan: Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-pakistan-nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi l\u1edbn khi c\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</h2><h2>Ch\u01b0a ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ee9c \u00e9p</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018, \u0110T U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia v\u00e0 Jordan. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1eadp l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-tran-mo-man-de-qua-cung-lo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan qu\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ch\u01b0a ch\u1eafc \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u1ea1i ch\u1ecbu \u00edt s\u1ee9c \u00e9p h\u01a1n v\u1edbi b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00e0 &quot;d\u1ec5&quot;. Pakistan v\u00e0 Nepal tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam, c\u00f2n Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n mang \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u1ea3i n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i U21. Gi\u1ea3i giao h\u1eefu t\u1ee9 h\u00f9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 mang t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t &quot;l\u00e0m n\u00f3ng&quot;, b\u1edfi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng d\u1ed1c h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ed7i lo b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c. Vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian th\u1eed l\u1eeda c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng v\u1eadn h\u00e0nh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01a1n tru khi ch\u1ecbu nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u1edf c\u00e1c v\u00f2ng sau.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t h\u01a1n, vi\u1ec7c \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong kh\u00e2u t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00ec &quot;sai s\u00f3t&quot; c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 \u00edt th\u1eddi gian l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c h\u01a1n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n sau m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm h\u01a1n n\u1eefa. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecf qua hai l\u1ea7n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c pha x\u1eed l\u00fd cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec1u thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Olympic-Viet-Nam-thang-Pakistan-Nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng hai l\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ea7n kh\u1eafc ph\u1ee5c khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n, g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. Khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00e0m b\u00e0n ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t \u00edt, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n ch\u1eaft chiu t\u1eebng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n t\u00e1i l\u1eadp th\u00e0nh t\u00edch nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1.</div>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai, \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tung v\u00e0o s\u00e2n thay cho Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng. Vi\u1ec7c ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 g\u1ed1c Tuy\u00ean Quang ph\u1ea3i ra ngh\u1ec9 s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi lo l\u1eafng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi nh\u1eefng b\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e1c s\u0129 ch\u0103m s\u00f3c c\u1ed5 ch\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng Pakistan Nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi \u0111\u1eb7t ra h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/Olympic-Viet-Nam-thang-Pakistan-Nhung-dau-hoi-dat-ra-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn thay th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \u0110\u1ed7 H\u00f9ng D\u0169ng v\u00e0 Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u k\u00e9o d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 ASIAD 2018, vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf nh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Park Hang Seo c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0111\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i ASIAD 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/thay-gi-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-30-olympic-pakistan-168-194498.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-van-chua-hai-long-du-thang-pakistan-168-194496.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng d\u00f9 th\u1eafng Pakistan</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/xuan-truong-dinh-chan-thuong-dt-olympic-viet-nam-nhan-tin-xau-292-194491.html\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam nh\u1eadn tin x\u1ea5u: Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/doi-tuyen-viet-nam/dt-olympic-viet-nam-thang-tran-mo-man-de-qua-cung-lo-292-194489.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n ASIAD 2018: D\u1ec5 qu\u00e1 c\u0169ng... lo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-sau-tran-thua-olympic-viet-nam-168-194488.html\">HLV Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn thua Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/link-xem-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-pakistan-372-194453.html\">Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 3-0 Olympic Pakistan (KT): M\u00e0n ra qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ea1t y\u00eau c\u1ea7u \u1edf ASIAD 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ea1t (TTVN)&nbsp;</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5505","checkdouble":"194503"},{"date":"07:48 15/08","title":"Lionel Messi t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/31/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Lionel Messi s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018 khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 x\u1ee9 Tango \u0111\u1eb7t ra c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi li\u1ec7u \"Leo\" \u0111ang t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf.</h2><h2>Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9, Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina t\u1eeb gi\u1edd \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018, ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t \u1edf b\u1ed1n tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu ti\u1ebfp theo. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y l\u00e0m d\u1ea5y l\u00ean nghi v\u1ea5n v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Messi \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/31/lionel-messi-khong-len-tuyen-argentina-da-giao-huu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lionel Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, \u0110T Argentina ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ph\u00e1p. HLV Jorge Sampaoli bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u00f2n Messi v\u1eabn gi\u1eef s\u1ef1 im l\u1eb7ng. Tr\u00ean th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Copa America 2016, &quot;Leo&quot; t\u1eebng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T Argentina nh\u01b0ng sau \u0111\u00f3 quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t ng\u00f4n vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 tr\u00ean AFP: &quot;\u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00edch h\u1ee3p, hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edfng s\u1ebd l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Messi&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Tevez th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m v\u1edbi Messi<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c Messi kh\u00f4ng l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Argentina \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft n\u0103m 2018, Carlos Tevez nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u00fd do c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Messi c\u1ea7n th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 suy ngh\u0129. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, ngay c\u1ea3 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p anh \u1ea5y quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Khi \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia thi \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u00f9 t\u1ed1t hay kh\u00f4ng, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch anh \u1ea5y. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadt t\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 v\u1edbi c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n Messi. Th\u1ebf n\u00ean t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, Messi v\u1eeba t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fat an \u1ee7i khi c\u00f9ng Barcelona gi\u00e0nh Si\u00eau C\u00fap T\u00e2y Ban Nha sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Sevilla. Chi\u1ebfc c\u00fap n\u00e0y c\u0169ng gi\u00fap Messi tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed Barcelona v\u1edbi 33 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Lionel Messi:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/vo-dich-sieu-cup-lionel-messi-lap-ky-luc-moi-trong-mau-ao-barca-180-194357.html\">V\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Si\u00eau C\u00fap, Lionel Messi l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/sevilla-vs-barca-sieu-cup-tbn-2018-dem-nay-372-194340.html\">Sevilla 1-2 Barca: Messi v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi b\u1eb1ng danh hi\u1ec7u Si\u00eau c\u00fap TBN</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-108-messi-chinh-thuc-tro-thanh-tan-doi-truong-barca-184-194199.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 10/8: Messi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/cuoc-chien-ronaldo-vs-messi-nong-lan-sang-ca-khoan-du-thuyen-188-193849.html\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn Ronaldo vs Messi n\u00f3ng lan sang c\u1ea3 kho\u1ea3n ... du thuy\u1ec1n</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/lionel-messi-va-dong-doi-lang-le-ve-hoi-quan-o-barcelona-188-192480.html\">Lionel Messi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1eb7ng l\u1ebd v\u1ec1 h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n \u1edf Barcelona</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/hau-truong/ngoi-sao-messi-tap-luyen-voi-cho-cung-truoc-mua-giai-moi-188-192416.html\">Ng\u00f4i sao Messi t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi ch\u00f3 c\u01b0ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5504","checkdouble":"194514"},{"date":"07:07 15/08","title":"Sergio Ramos: \"Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/15/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Sergio Ramos l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1edbi l\u1eddi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid v\u1eabn s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</h2><h2>Kh\u00f4ng Ronaldo, kh\u00f4ng sao c\u1ea3<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Atletico t\u1ea1i Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Real Madrid l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009 s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i. Cr7 \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Juventus trong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergio Ramos l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sergio Ramos l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/15/sergio-ramos-len-tieng-ve-cristiano-ronaldo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Sergio Ramos l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Los Blancos c\u00f3 c\u00f2n m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi thi\u1ebfu Ronaldo, Sergio Ramos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &quot;B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i nh\u00ecn s\u00e2u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat. \u1ede \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n coi nhau nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh. Ch\u00eca kh\u00f3a d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n gi\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t gia \u0111\u00ecnh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;M\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ng\u1eebng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y x\u1ea3y ra nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u1eabn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Real Madrid v\u1eabn th\u1ebf th\u00f4i, ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ng\u0103n ch\u00fang t\u00f4i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o Jurgen Klopp<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2017-18, Sergio Ramos \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7y tinh qu\u00e1i khi\u1ebfn Mohamed Salah d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. M\u1ea5t Salah, Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid, HLV Jurgen Klopp sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u li\u00ean t\u1ee5c c\u00f4ng k\u00edch Ramos \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn b\u00e2y gi\u1edd.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp m\u00f4 t\u1ea3 Sergio Ramos l\u00e0 &quot;t\u00e0n nh\u1eabn v\u00e0 t\u00e0n b\u1ea1o&quot;, g\u1ecdi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 &quot;tay \u0111\u00f4 v\u1eadt&quot;. \u0110\u00e1p l\u1ea1i, Sergio Ramos cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o v\u1ec1 Salah n\u1eefa, quan \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ti\u1ebfp thu&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef tay Salah nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y n\u00edu t\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a bao gi\u1edd c\u1ed1 l\u00e0m \u0111au b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. Klopp mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ec7n minh cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft nh\u01b0ng n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e2u ph\u1ea3i l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u00f4ng \u1ea5y thua \u1edf chung k\u1ebft&quot;.<br>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 Real Madrid m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018-19:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-lopetegui-muon-no-bom-tan-bld-real-noi-khong-180-194507.html\">HLV Lopetegui mu\u1ed1n n\u1ed5 bom t\u1ea5n, BL\u0110 Real n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-148-mu-bat-ngo-muon-chieu-mo-leroy-sane-phien-ban-20-184-194502.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 14/8: M.U b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Leroy Sane &ldquo;phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n 2.0&rdquo;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/nguoi-dai-dien-bao-tin-buon-cho-real-vu-modric-180-194480.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Real v\u1ee5 Modric</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-tinh-chi-60-trieu-euro-mua-pjanic-180-194470.html\">Real t\u00ednh chi 60 tri\u1ec7u euro mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o nh\u1ea5t Serie A</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-chot-marcos-alonso-thay-marcelo-180-194461.html\">Real ch\u1ed1t sao Chelsea thay Marcelo</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/3-doi-bong-anh-muon-co-than-dong-cua-real-madrid-180-194418.html\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>